name: Major Highway-rail inter modal facilities, United States, 2007
description: This dataset displays the point location of the major highway-rail inter modal freight facilities in the continental USA. This data was processed using the latitude and the longitude coordinates associated with each point. This data was accessed on January 29, 2008 from the Bureau of Transportation Statistics at: http://www.bts.gov/publications/north_american_transportation_atlas_data/
